Package edu.kit.unwwi.checkpoints.qmp

Schnittstelle Command

Alle bekannten Implementierungsklassen:
Continue, ELFDump, QHMCommand, QueryBlock, QueryCPU, QueryRegisters, QueryTLB, Status, Stop
public interface Command
An interface representing a command. Such a command can be given to the interface to transmission and will then receive a result, which each command then can parse by itself.

    • receiveResult

      default void receiveResult(@NotNull @NotNull Object result) throws IllegalStateException
      This method takes the received JSON and then may or may not parse it in any way fit to its purpose. It may also fully discard it if not needed. Should probably not be used outside QMPInterface.
      Parameter:
      result - The result received from QEMU.
      Löst aus:
      IllegalStateException - Gets thrown when this command may only be executed once.
